room_title: Escape room "Wiseguy Lounge" by Exit 4 Private Escape Rooms in Collingswood
room_description: It’s 1979 and you’re part of the infamous crew that robbed JFK airport of over 5 million dollars. The architect of the plan has been making anyone associated with the robbery ‘disappear’ and you have one hour to break into his restaurant and find your cut of the money and get out before he returns to make you ‘disappear’ as well.
